➜乌鲁木齐清雪效率获国内众多网友点赞
http://www.sohu.com/a/436020216_118570	28295
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20201203/93f7611887b348de9009dd571f986429.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20201203/40690a1f820f4b97975cb49cc4da1956.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20201203/b797f68561bd42edb74608bd53ef20ce.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20201203/ed2602bd5fd04bf189580bea19d2655f.jpeg" max-width="600"><span class="img-desc" style="font-size: 16px;">新疆网抖音号关于乌鲁木齐清雪的短视频及获得众多网友点赞、关注。（网页截图）</span></img></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
<div class="lookall-shadow"></div>
